---
title: Rotisserie-Inspired Chicken with Potato Wedges and Creamy Ranch Coleslaw
description: Our DIY spice rub combines sweetness, saltiness, smokiness, earthiness and zestiness! All of this balanced flavour is spread over chicken breasts to create a succulent main that's further elevated by a savoury gravy.
